description:
Primary Responsibilities 

Design and implement Securities trading and settlement systems as well as wealth management systems for the global financial market; 
Gather user requirements, analyze and design systems; 
Work with multiple teams on projects; 
Provide operational support.

 Requirements 

2+ year of software development working experience; 
Candidates with lesser experience will be considered for junior position;
Strong analytical and problem solving skill; 
Hands-on experience in MS Visual Studio, C#/VB.Net / ASP.NET, Winform, SQL; 
Familiar with the Securities Industry, or working experience in brokerage firm/ bank will be an advantage. 

 Character 

Passionate to build great software solution; 
Willing to learn, and self-motivated; 
Good team player. 

We assemble passionate people who build solution smartly.  We leverage cutting edge technologies to get things ready. And we are looking forward to you, the talented person, to join us.  Please email your detailed resume with current, expected salary and availability by clicking “Apply Now”.

No recruitment agencies please.

Job Responsibilities:

Responsible for development, implementation and testing of web application and responsive website with CMS backend;
Provide support on user acceptance test and system maintenance;
Work closely with UI/UX designer and eCommerce team to deliver the best experience on both web and mobile platforms; and
Troubleshoot and resolve application production issues.

Requirements:

Higher Diploma / Associate Degree or above in Computer Science, Information Technology, or any related disciplines;
2+ years’ experience in web application development;
Strong & hands-on development skills in WordPress, WooCommerce, PHP, CSS, JavaScript, MySQL, and responsive web;
Familiar with SEO, Google Analytics, Git, Bootstrap, Angular, Drupal, and Wix would be an advantage;
Good analytical and problem-solving skills;
Aggressive, self-motivated, result-orientated, and able to work under pressure;
Excellent interpersonal and communication skills; and
Good command of Cantonese, English, and Mandarin.

Casetify is looking for a Senior UXUI designer experienced in information architecture, interaction, and user testing to join our team. You will collaborate with the E-commerce team to design and build next generation Web/mobile applications. The right candidates will be excellent communicators, comfortable in a high-velocity startup, and passionate about creating products that transform people’s lifestyle.
Responsibilities:
Prepare UX/UI design and materials including wire framing, mockup and rapid prototyping for various interfaces, including websites, mobile devices and apps for ecommerce site;
Analyze current user journey to understand motivation, expose pain points, issues and improvement opportunities;
Conduct user research, A/B testing, and propose solutions to optimize customer experience;
Communicate concepts and work collaboratively with project team / Tech team in order to develop the most efficient design schemas;
Sit with developers to do pixel-perfect reviews of frontend products before they are pushed in production;
Consume our Design System library and contribute to its evolution.
Requirements:


Bachelor Degree in Creative Media / Interactive Design / Web Design / Web Development;
5+ years of experience building transactional website;
Specific experience in a fast growing ecommerce company;
Ability to solve problems of complexity through smart design;
Being data-driven, and be able to back up your assertions with data, with proficiency in analytic tools - Hotjar, Google Analytics, Optimizely etc;
A user-first attitude and ensure we consistently deliver a user-centric culture;
Strong understanding of web grids and browser limitations;
Familiarity with usability testing, A/B testing methods;
Proficiency with Photoshop, Adobe XD, Webflow, HTML, CSS, PHP;
Bouns: Experience with Shopify site designs / SDK.
Please include 2 URLs of your Open Source, personal projects into your resume.

To cope with our continuous growth and business expansion, we are looking for energetic and high calibre of candidates to join. 

Duties:


Responsible for user interface design of system, mobile apps and websites
Banner, image retouch and other graphics design


Requirements:


Diploma holder or above in Web / Multimedia / Graphics design or related discipline;
At least 3 years’ solid experience in Web/App/Multimedia design;
Proficiency in graphics & web design tools such as Adobe Photoshop,  Illustrator, XD or Sketch;
Knowledge of design, prototyping tools and usability best practices in wire frames and prototypes;
Strong sense on responsive design, UI/UX and technology trends;
Knowledge of iOS & Android app official UI guideline;
Knowledge of JavaScript, HTML5, CSS3 is a plus;
Responsible, detail-minded, have good interpersonal and communication skills;
Immediately available is preferable;
Candidates with more experience will be considered as Senior UX/UI Designer

At least 3 portfolios provided for review is a must

Interested parties, please send full resume with CURRENT & EXPECTED SALARY to Centaline Data Technology Limited.

Responsibilities

Development and deployment of websites and/or web-based applications;
Implement appropriate and tidy codes and test them in various environments, enhance and/or modify them if necessary;
Follow standardized procedures to ensure the smoothness of development;
Handle multiple projects simultaneously in a timely and professional manner.

Requirements

Diploma, associate degree or bachelor degree in Computer Science, I.T. or related disciplines;
1-2 years relevant working experience in related fields;
Solid knowledge in web technologies and frameworks: HTML, SCSS, jQuery, PHP, MySQL, Bootstrap, Symfony;
Proficiency in front-end development would be a bonus;
Self-motivated, energetic and passionate in exploring new technology;
Strong problem solving, interpersonal & communication skills and team player;
Ability to work under pressure by handling multiple assignments and meeting tight deadlines;
Detailed mind, proactive and willing to take responsibility;
Fresh graduates will also be considered
Immediate availability would be a high priority. 

We offer:

5-day work
Medical Insurance
Young and joyful working environment
Comprehensive training and career development opportunities

Interested parties please send your application with a full resume stating your present and expected salary to the Company.

JOIN OUR CHICLE'S FAMILY. APPLY NOW!

**All information will be used for recruitment purposes only**

Job Responsibilities:

Work closely with both internal and external parties to manage the e-commerce site to ensure the success of all deliverables as per schedule;
Manage new features implementation from collecting user requirements, defining project scope, specification, timeline/resource, and final testing;
Manage third party and external providers’ contracts and Statement of Work;
Track project deliverables and prepare reports defining project progress, issues and solutions;
Optimize user experience on various devices according to best practices;
Constantly strive for new/innovated ideas and solutions for the business & improve operation efficiency of the team;
Propose solutions with options to solve the problems arising out of the website development;
Support ecommerce operation on routine operation tasks

 Requirement

Degree holder in Computer Science, IT or other related discipline
At least 4 years relevant experience in E-commerce website management
Proficient PC skills in MS Excel, Word and Power Point
Experience in Magento is an advantage
Ability to handle multi-task, target-oriented, work under pressure and meet deadlines required
Work independently, self-motivated, detail-minded, good attitude, strong sense of responsibility
Good team player and good in communicating with different levels within the organization
Good command in both oral and written English, Cantonese and Mandarin

We offer 5-day work week, medical and dental insurance, MPF, bank holidays and competitive remuneration package to the right candidate.

All information collected will be used for recruitment related purpose only and will be treated in strict confidence. Applicants who are not notified within 8 weeks may consider their application unsuccessful. All applications will be retained for maximum 6 months and will be destroyed.

