Responsibilities:

Design user interface for Portal, POS, Customer Frontends (Mobile Apps, Tablet, PC);
Design for UI and UX;
Collaborate with our development team to bring your designs to live;
Communicate with clients to gather requirements and present design concept.

Requirements:

Degree Holder in digital design or related disciplines;
Minimum 1 year of UI /UX design experience (especially on web and Mobile App), or equivalent experience;
Experience designing intuitive user experiences based on requirements;
Proficiency in graphic design - familiar with Photoshop or AI;
Proficiency in prototyping tools like Sketch, Figma;
Passionate to provide innovative, creative and reliable digital business solutions (web, app, system) to our clients;
Good team player with strong growth mindset, excellent communication, work with strict deadlines and under high-pressure situations;
Good command of spoken and written English, Chinese and Mandarin;
Candidate with more experience will be considered as SeniorUX/UI Designer;
Immediate availability or short notice is highly preferred.

We offer attractive salary and fringe benefits to the right candidate.  Interested candidates should send FULL RESUME with Current & Expected salary.

Data collected will be used for recruitment purpose only.

Responsibilities:

Analyse user requirements to design and implement test plan, and ensure test coverage;
Respond feature test, integration test and performance test of systems;
Provide test result record and track issue status updates/status;
Support and coordinate closely with internal teams to understand user requirements;
Report and provide feedback to make improvement in the quality of deliverable as well as the QA process;
Assist in the implementation of quality assurance operation or additional work flow updates or process;
Ad hoc involvement in tasks or projects as assigned by supervisor/team leader.

Requirements:

Degree Holder in Computer Science, Information Technology, or related disciplines;
Minimum 2 years working experience in quality assurance or software testing, with F&B or retails exposure is a definite advantage;
Experience in test tool (i.e. Postman, Chrome Dev Tools etc.);
Strong knowledge in QA process and methodology;
Excellent analytical, problem solving, and documentation skills;
Fast learner, self-motivated, responsible and a good team player;
Good command of spoken and written English, Chinese and Mandarin;
Immediate availability or short notice is highly preferred.

We offer attractive salary and fringe benefits to the right candidate.  Interested candidates should send FULL RESUME with Current & Expected salary.


